15 WHEREAS, the Safety Impact Award emphasizes the importance of education, training, and
16 community engagement in promoting safe and responsible firearm ownership; and
17 WHEREAS, Colt is further committed to encouraging secure storage solutions to prevent
18 unauthorized access to firearms and accidents; and
19 WHEREAS, Colt supports education and training initiatives for individuals of all experience
20 levels to foster a culture of safety and accountability.
21 NOW, THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED BY THE HOUSE OF REPRESENTATIVES that
22 the members of this body commend Colt's Manufacturing Company for its unwavering
23 commitment to promoting safe and responsible firearms ownership and for its efforts to
24 enhance community education and engagement through the Safety Impact Award and other
25 initiatives.
26 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that the Clerk of the House of Representatives is authorized
27 and directed to make an appropriate copy of this resolution available for distribution to Colt's
28 Manufacturing Company.
